Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 芽芽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.96,0:11:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.17,0:11:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.26,0:11:13.22,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.93,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,好像已經實現了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:19.26,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:22.85,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,和仁太媽媽做了個約定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和…媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.02,0:11:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只有一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:30.02,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.61,0:11:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}仁太他都不哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}可能 是因為我變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.95,0:11:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}他一直都在強撐著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:39.07,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}阿姨…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}雖然很期待投胎轉世
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是只有這個我還不放心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}讓他忍受了那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}其實希望他能多笑一些 多生氣一些 多哭一些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:56.68,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:11:59.97,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}芽芽和阿姨約定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:02.14,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一定要讓仁太哭出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.19,0:12:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}謝謝你 小芽芽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}那就拜託你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:15.90,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:20.12,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:26.83,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽想破了腦袋都不知道該怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:28.54,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:32.42,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,才想要拜託大家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:34.96,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,就打電話讓大家出來集合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.59,0:12:38.76,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我沒打算讓大家欺負你讓你哭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:41.14,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽腦子笨嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:46.39,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,…想要找到一個不欺負你就能讓你哭的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:47.68,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,那天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在回這裡之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直想要實現的願望是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:53.07,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 果然還是…沒能順利完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.65,0:12:59.53,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是因為瞞著仁太 所以才受到懲罰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是什麼懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當然會去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞞不瞞著我都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論什麼時候 無論什麼事情 我都會去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.29,0:13:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:14.84,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 你又哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:22.26,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢 其實芽芽還是喜歡仁太的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:28.06,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多 要說再見了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 現在還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以只和我說再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直都很想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想叫你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想對你說 我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:49.12,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,仁太…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 大家都是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家也都很喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:13:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家也都想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:14:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家在等著你 等著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那個屬於我們的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:20.05,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要實現你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:24.72,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡仁太了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這麼突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:29.91,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想永遠和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:37.98,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎想要永遠和仁太這樣下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仁…仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:49.49,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,仁…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽 芽芽！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁太！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道芽芽她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:14:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:00.58,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,仁…太…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀 你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.84,0:15:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:15.18,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,來…來玩捉迷藏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩…玩什麼捉迷藏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仁太 芽芽…在玩捉迷藏嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 芽芽！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捉迷藏？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 仁太！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.74,0:15:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽——！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我們也去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.07,0:15:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:39.62,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒…還沒好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:47.17,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒…和大家好好道別…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽——！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:54.76,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒好哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:15:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:15:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:01.37,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒好哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:04.77,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒好哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芽芽——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:11.78,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒好…再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:17.94,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,再等…一下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仁太？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.22,0:16:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 芽芽…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的腳…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:37.85,Meiko,,0000,0000,0000,,仁太…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然 芽芽已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日記的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個字是…芽芽？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
