Dialogue: 2,0:23:22.61,0:23:33.98,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,800)\blur5}I'm following you everywhere you go
Dialogue: 3,0:23:35.61,0:23:39.36,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,800)\blur5}Still...
Dialogue: 4,0:23:39.54,0:23:45.73,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,800)\blur5}Inside a funny dream
Dialogue: 5,0:23:46.67,0:23:57.97,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,800)\blur5}I'm soaked in tears everywhere I go
Dialogue: 6,0:23:59.73,0:24:04.98,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,800)\blur5}Caught up in this world
Dialogue: 7,0:24:04.63,0:24:10.39,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,800)\blur5}Like in a daydream
Dialogue: 8,0:24:10.25,0:24:14.64,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,800)\blur5}Lost in your smile
Dialogue: 9,0:24:15.51,0:24:20.90,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,800)\blur5}But I wake up to a lonely daen
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.41,0:24:25.33,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,800)\blur5}To know you're gone
Dialogue: 1,0:24:25.77,0:24:32.06,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,800)\blur5}My endless love...
